d/f of rolling updates & rollbacks

-------Rolling updates:
rolling updates gradually replace the pods without users facing any downtime

Rooling backs------
if new version failes, Roll back to previous version if something goes wrong



kubectl rollout history deployment/myapp
kubectl rollout undo deployment/myapp
kubectl rollout undo deployment/myapp --to-revision=2
kubectl rollout status deployment/myapp
kubectl get pods

_______________________
helm history myapp
helm rollback myapp 3
